Package avdta.vehicle

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Bus
    This vehicle travels along a fixed route, updating travel times on relevant BusLinks as it travels.
    DriverType
    This class (a user-defined data type) stores the name (AV or HV), reaction time, and whether the type is AV or not.
    PersonalVehicle
    This represents a privately-owned vehicle.
    Vehicle
    Represents a (single) vehicle in the network.
    VehTime
    This is a tuple of a Vehicle and an arrival time.
    VOT
    This class calculates a value of time distribution based on the Dagum income distribution
